{"Sid":0,"Did":118130,"Id":"282277","Title":"頭城忠孝新村天后宮戲台","ImageUrl":"https://dcm.s3.hicloud.net.tw/excel/place/2020-02-24/d8bcb89b-5364-472e-b2a1-718bfe1349c7/collection/80de9d79-1f49-496e-bcea-fa62a9815b60/108-her-pa-1812-201910252246355db2e16a5063c0.jpg / https://dcm.s3.hicloud.net.tw/excel/place/2020-02-24/d8bcb89b-5364-472e-b2a1-718bfe1349c7/collection/dda20e96-c427-4074-9f05-86531a9e460c/108-her-pa-1812-201910252246355db2e16a5063c1.jpg","IndexCode":"Culture_Place","CustomColumns":{"Description":"\n\n頭城忠孝新村天后宮的戲台設置在廟前，為鋼筋混凝土構造，前半段開敞無牆，後半段則有牆面，上端疊砌圓洞型水泥花磚，以利於通風與採光。 　　此座戲台最大的特色在於其手繪彩磁。在戲台基座前方有一幅題為「富貴双壽」的彩磁，主要是由兩隻綬帶鳥與數朵俗稱富貴花的牡丹花所構成。另在中脊樑與背牆間之橫樑則貼飾以八仙綵主題之手繪彩磁。戲台背牆則是同樣以手繪彩磁呈現之天后宮樂捐芳名錄，中央主要畫面則是以「福祿壽三仙」為主題。戲台手繪彩磁是由宜蘭知名藝師「景陽畫室」顏文伯所繪燒，相當具有特色。\n\n","Keyword_Rights_2":"CC BY / CC BY","Keyword_Des_Rights_2":"CC0","Keyword_Longitude":"121.886634","Keyword_Latitude":"24.935827","Original_Url":"https://cmsdb.culture.tw/place/A3180825-CFAF-4532-A296-A5CE979E221B","Original_Identifier":"282277","Keyword_Subject_1":"民俗與宗教","alias":"","Keywords":"大陳 / 天后宮 / 忠孝新村 / 景陽畫室 / 頭城 / 戲台 / 顏文伯","historicalDates":"","LastUpdateTime":"2020/02/24 15:11:18","timelines":"","place":"頭城鎮忠孝新村","address":"宜蘭縣頭城鎮忠孝新村54號","longitude":"121.886634","latitude":"24.935827","phone":"","Event":"","relationPeople":"","open":"0","free":"否","openTime":"","openTimeDescription":"","capacity":"","traffic":"","subjection":"","tag":"","situation":"","historicalDataBrief":"","historicalData":"","reference":"","writer":"林世傑/ 蔡明志","createOrgName":"宜蘭縣政府文化局","source":"","Keyword_Rights_1":"","AllImages":"https://dcm.s3.hicloud.net.tw/excel/place/2020-02-24/d8bcb89b-5364-472e-b2a1-718bfe1349c7/collectionOpen/e7b9b27e-1ec5-415b-b726-f4070cf9b1c5/108-her-pa-1812-re-201910252247585db2e16a5063c0.jpg / https://dcm.s3.hicloud.net.tw/excel/place/2020-02-24/d8bcb89b-5364-472e-b2a1-718bfe1349c7/collectionOpen/20eed4f7-b22c-4b8c-8849-86a821b8b5cf/108-her-pa-1812-re-201910252247585db2e16a5063c1.jpg"}}